Dialogs.Text: SecurPink1850: There is more people to talk with around here? This place seems quite lonely these days.
MsMaki95: Yeah, here you have me. >-o
SecurPink1850: I mean... If there is more people around.
MsMaki95: I know, i know, just messing with you. xD
MsMaki95: I'm here with the people of my 2D server and a friend of mine.
SecurPink1850: I see, seems quite some people are interested back in this place.
MsMaki95: It's not all the server that comes here though, but the ones that come are regular here. And we are all friendly. n-n
MsMaki95: Also, some more people came here that are not from the server. An oldie just like you and... Well... I don't know how to put this. o-O
MsMaki95: Yeah, they call themselves a Sun cult... Or something like that. Probably a bunch of little kids playing. Un-n
Thomas B: Little kids? Here? I can buy they are a bunch of grown men playing weird games.
Thomas B: So there is a small group of colorful people around here. Seems i won't be alone during this investigation.
